---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Yukun" noIndex={true}>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] space-y-4">
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you submit an RFQ or sample request through our website, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, company name, email address, country, and phone number (if provided)</li>
          <li>Product interests and technical requirements you share with us</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiry with product recommendations and quotations</li>
          <li>Process sample requests and orders</li>
          <li>Communicate about your project requirements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>Form submissions are processed through Web3Forms and stored securely. We retain inquiry data for the duration of our business relationship plus a reasonable period for record-keeping.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website does not use tracking cookies. We may use essential session cookies for form functionality.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@yukun-drive.com" class="text-[var(--color-brand-light)]">info@yukun-drive.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
